                        "effect": "The boggards execute coordinated melee attacks against each enemy in a 5-foot emanation, with a DC 21 basic Reflex save. The damage dealt depends on the number of actions.   \n [#] 1d6 bludgeoning or piercing damage   \n [##] 2d6+7 bludgeoning or piercing damage   \n [###] 2d6+11 bludgeoning or piercing damage"
